{
  "stem": "7781.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they came for lunch, or for the day, and we gave them the cards, and it was a big thing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You think like this, you go into the supermarket, and you buy whatever you want.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In those days, you couldn't buy it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was not-- it wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we established-- slowly, we established a community, a Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We took it-- there were 17 Hungarian girls in the hospital, and we took them out, too.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Each one found a cousin, and we went to the-- to the English officer, and he introduces another cousin.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the German, as we were walking for food, I-- we would walk in, get the ration, you know, whatever they put on your plate, eat, walk out, and walk around, and walk again.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, the-- the-- there were German girls who worked there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were serving.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they got wise to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they say, you just walked by.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So one of us went to the German-- to the English commanding officer and had a talk with him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I, to the guy, said, listen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We walked two times through, but we-- we suffered so much during the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she didn't want to give us any food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She refused.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So the-- the English officer called together all the personnel, and they told them, any time they walk by, you give them food.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was very nice of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And because we were used to-- you know, to all-- and here, we show the concern about one human being to the other human being, and it was very nice of him.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so we-- we got all stragglers, you know, from all over, and we got together, and we formed a Jewish community in the city of [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we had our own restaurant.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
